<h2 id="字体"><a href="#字体" class="headerlink" title="字体"></a>字体</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 加粗</span></span><br><span class="line">**这是加粗**</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 删除线</span></span><br><span class="line">~~被删除字体~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 斜体</span></span><br><span class="line">*这是斜体*</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 这是斜体加粗</span></span><br><span class="line">***斜体加粗***</span><br><span class="line">---斜体加粗---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>&#x2F;&#x2F; 加粗<br><strong>这是加粗</strong><br>&#x2F;&#x2F; 删除线<br><del>被删除字体</del><br>&#x2F;&#x2F; 斜体<br><em>这是斜体</em><br>&#x2F;&#x2F; 这是斜体加粗<br><em><strong>斜体加粗</strong></em></p>
<h2 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 引用语法</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;作者：谁谁谁</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;作者：谁谁谁</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;作者：谁谁谁</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>&#x2F;&#x2F; 引用语法</p>
<blockquote>
