<h2 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//分割线</span></span><br><span class="line">* * * </span><br><span class="line">- - -</span><br><span class="line">------</span><br><span class="line">******</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 都可作为分割线</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

